  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWe need a way to calculate message count and memory occupation of messages in FSM's mailbox.\r\n\r\nYou can add a method in [msg.rs](https://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/master/components/raftstore/src/store/msg.rs) to return the memory size of msg. And mutate the metrics before it's enqueued and after it's dequeued.\r\n\r\nYou probably should use local metrics to reduce performance impact. You can refer [local_metrics](https://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/master/components/raftstore/src/store/local_metrics.rs) to see how local metrics work.\r\n\r\n## Difficulty\r\n\r\n- Medium\r\n\r\n## Score\r\n\r\n- 605\r\n\r\n## Mentor(s)\r\n\r\n- @BusyJay \r\n- @zhangjinpeng1987\r\n\r\n## Recommended Skills\r\n\r\n- Rust\r\n\r\n## Learning Materials\r\n",
